name: Jeffy Game
description:
Jeffy Game is a fan game of SuperMarioLogan, while having Non-SML related content!

----

Jeffy & his 2 friends where testing Cody's New Invention. But It went wrong as it made another clone called "Effy". Then Effy jumped out of the window & took a random person, Which is Lammy. it's up to Jeffy to safe her. But also have to fight enemys.
